Sliɣ i yemma-s tuɣwas. 
Tezza tasa n tyemmat taqbaylit.
Ttqadareɣ yemma akked baba. 
Taqbaylit ɣer yemma itt-ṭḍeɣ. 
Yufeg uqermud, yeɛra uxxam. 
Yuɣal useksut i tasilt. 
Yebda yettfuṛu seksu. 
Lɛerc n At jennad. 
Lɛerc n At zmenzer. 
Lɛerc n At wagennun. 
Lɛerc n Iḥesnawen. 
Lɛerc n At ɛisi.
Lɛerc n At yiraten.
Amussu n leɛrac yessergagi adabu azzayri. 
Adabu yewwet ḥala mi yessedrem amussu n leɛrac.
Ass-mi tendeh tefsut taberkant lliɣ di tseddawit. 
Yenna-d tidet yekcem ɣer lḥebs. 
Ruɣ seg teḍsa. 
Keč d bu uxlul. 
Ttxil-k ḥbes tuksa n ixenčuren s ufus! 
Yeffeɣ-ik laɛqel ɣef idrimen. 
Yeffeɣ-ikem laɛqel ɣef idrimen. 
Sufɣen-as laɛqel yedrimen. 
Yessufeɣ laɛqel i baba-s ɣef idrimen. 
Ziɣ tedrewceḍ! 
Ziɣ tebbehbaḍ! 
Ziɣ truḥeḍ deg-sent! 
Ziɣ tmexleḍ! 
Ziɣ ixuṣ-ik ubulun! 
Ziɣ ur d-yegra deg-k wara! 
Ziɣ tekfiḍ! 
Ziɣ cwiyya-k kan deg-ki!
Ziɣ teqqerseḍ! 
Ziɣ qeṛsen-ak lexyuḍ!
Ziɣ tettwazedɣeḍ! 
Ziɣ ulac deg wallaɣ-ik! 
Ziɣ yeffeɣ-ik laɛqel! 
Ziɣ yuffeg-ak uqermud!
Ziɣ ur mazal deg-k acemma! 
Ziɣ aḥlil deg-k! 
Ziɣ aḥlil fell-ak!
Ziɣ yekfa ssuq-ik! 
Ziɣ yif-ik wulac! 
Ziɣ allaɣ-ik d ilem! 
Ziɣ iqqur uqeṛṛuy-ik! 
Ziɣ tetxetxeḍ! 
Ziɣ txelxleḍ! 
Ziɣ tṭeẓṭeẓeḍ! 
Ziɣ tetaxdeḍ! 
Ziɣ tetnakeḍ! 
Ziɣ tčefčefeḍ! 
Ziɣ ahbub! 
Yesla-iyi-d mi s-nniɣ ala. 
Yesla-iyi-d mi s-nniɣ ih. 
Dayen, berka-aɣ tmesxir! 
Dayen akeɛrer fell-i ad k-yehdu ṛebbi!
I yuɣen irgazen ur ttrun! 
Yewwet-it s taqabact ɣer uqeṛṛuy. 
Yewwet-it s tefḍist ɣer uqeṛṛuy.
Yewwet-it s umger ɣer uqeṛṛuy.
Yewwet-it s lmus ɣer uqeṛṛuy.
Aqenduṛ, tačamart ma d aqarruy yenneḍ-as taɛmamt. 
Ḥemleɣ-tt ma d nettat tekreh-iyi. 
Testewtiw-as iḍ d wass. 
Yestewtiw-as iḍ d wass. 






